{"id":6390,"date":"2024-10-13T19:15:18","date_gmt":"2024-10-13T19:15:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gei.thomsuninfocare.com\/?p=6390"},"modified":"2025-06-18T12:31:40","modified_gmt":"2025-06-18T12:31:40","slug":"dr-divya-giridhar","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/dr-divya-giridhar\/","title":{"rendered":"Dr. Divya Giridhar"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-1 fusion-flex-container has-pattern-background has-mask-background nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-content-wrap\" style=\"max-width:1414.4px;margin-left: calc(-4% \/ 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% \/ 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-0 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-padding-top:40px;--awb-padding-bottom:50px;--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:20px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-1 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Educational Qualifications<\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-separator\" style=\"align-self: flex-start;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;max-width:20%;\"><div class=\"fusion-separator-border sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"--awb-height:20px;--awb-amount:20px;--awb-sep-color:var(--awb-color4);border-color:var(--awb-color4);border-top-width:2px;\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-1\"><p>Dr. Divya Giridhar completed her Bachelor of Medicine and Bachelor of Surgery from MOSC Medical College, Kerala, in 2013, followed by a Compulsory Rotational Internship there from January 2014 to January 2015. She pursued her M.S. in Ophthalmology at Christian Medical College, Vellore, under Dr. MGR Medical University, graduating in March 2020. She then trained as a Fellow in Cornea and Refractive Services at Sankara Nethralaya, Chennai (January 2022 &#8211; December 2023) and completed a Short-Term Phaco Training at M.N. Eye Hospital, Chennai, in May 2024.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-2 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-top:40px;--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Specialisation<\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-separator\" style=\"align-self: flex-start;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;max-width:20%;\"><div class=\"fusion-separator-border sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"--awb-height:20px;--awb-amount:20px;--awb-sep-color:var(--awb-color4);border-color:var(--awb-color4);border-top-width:2px;\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-2\"><p>She specializes in managing various Cornea Disorders, including Corneal Infections, Dry Eye, Ocular Surface Disorders, Allergic Eye Disease, and Cataract Surgery. She is also skilled in Corneal Transplantation.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-3 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-top:40px;--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Work Experience<\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-separator\" style=\"align-self: flex-start;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;max-width:20%;\"><div class=\"fusion-separator-border sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"--awb-height:20px;--awb-amount:20px;--awb-sep-color:var(--awb-color4);border-color:var(--awb-color4);border-top-width:2px;\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-3\"><p>Dr. Divya Giridhar gained extensive experience through her 24-month Cornea Fellowship at Sankara Nethralaya, Chennai. She also served as a Senior Resident at Giridhar Eye Institute in Cochin from November 2020 to December 2021 and worked as a PG Registrar at Schell Eye Hospital, CMC Vellore, during her postgraduate training (April 2017 &#8211; March 2020).<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-4 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-top:40px;--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Publications<\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-separator\" style=\"align-self: flex-start;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;max-width:20%;\"><div class=\"fusion-separator-border sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"--awb-height:20px;--awb-amount:20px;--awb-sep-color:var(--awb-color4);border-color:var(--awb-color4);border-top-width:2px;\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-4\"><p>She has contributed to several notable publications, including:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Corneal scarring after epithelium-off collagen cross-linking, Indian Journal of Ophthalmology, 2024.<\/li>\n<li>Bilateral Corneal Ulcers and Endophthalmitis After Eyelid Surgery, TNOA Journal of Ophthalmic Science and Research, 2022.<\/li>\n<li>Conjunctival necrosis due to periocular clear steroid injection, Journal of Cornea and Ocular Surface, 2023.<\/li>\n<li>Successful outcome with injection bleomycin in primary lymphangioma of the conjunctiva, Indian Journal of Ophthalmology &#8211; Case Reports, 2023.<\/li>\n<li>Possible IgG4-related disease in a case of necrotizing scleritis, Indian Journal of Ophthalmology &#8211; Case Reports, 2022.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-5 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-top:40px;--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Achievements<\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-separator\" style=\"align-self: flex-start;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;max-width:20%;\"><div class=\"fusion-separator-border sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"--awb-height:20px;--awb-amount:20px;--awb-sep-color:var(--awb-color4);border-color:var(--awb-color4);border-top-width:2px;\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-5\"><p>Dr. Giridhar has actively presented her work at various National and State Conferences, including KSOS, TNOA, and AIOS. Notably, she presented a paper on Unmet Needs and Functional Status of Adults with Presbyopia at KSOS Dhristi 2021, a study on KPRO swap in MOOKP at the AIOS 2023, and an e-poster on Spectacle Use Patterns in Rural South India at the 67th Tamil Nadu Ophthalmic Association Annual Conference, showcasing her dedication to advancing knowledge in her field.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-2 fusion-flex-container nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling fusion-animated\" style=\"--awb-background-position:right center;--awb-border-sizes-top:0px;--awb-border-sizes-bottom:0px;--awb-border-sizes-left:0px;--awb-border-sizes-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-padding-top:30px;--awb-padding-right:30px;--awb-padding-bottom:65px;--awb-padding-left:30px;--awb-padding-top-small:125.863px;--awb-margin-top:0px;--awb-margin-bottom:0px;--awb-margin-bottom-medium:145px;--awb-ba